                            <comment id="14383277" author="guozhang" created="Fri, 27 Mar 2015 03:17:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just updated the protocol wiki with the new version. As for merging &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1841&quot; title=&quot;OffsetCommitRequest API - timestamp field is not versioned&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-1841&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-1841&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, I can do that after 04/06; if that is too late some one can pick it up.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14384234" author="jjkoshy" created="Fri, 27 Mar 2015 17:49:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Reopening since we need to merge &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1841&quot; title=&quot;OffsetCommitRequest API - timestamp field is not versioned&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-1841&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-1841&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14385848" author="junrao" created="Sun, 29 Mar 2015 16:49:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Perhaps, we can do &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1841&quot; title=&quot;OffsetCommitRequest API - timestamp field is not versioned&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-1841&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-1841&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; together with &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-2068&quot; title=&quot;Replace OffsetCommit Request/Response with  org.apache.kafka.common.requests  equivalent&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-2068&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-2068&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. There will probably be less duplicated code that way.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14387358" author="jjkoshy" created="Mon, 30 Mar 2015 20:41:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes I think that makes more sense&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
